column5: Congrats on your first pike.
congrats on ur first pike!  Wait til u catch a monster one, and its so damn scary looking you want to get ur hand near its mouth!
Careful,  Those things are addictive
No problem Photoz....but you are going to be there...
Wow...that's quite the story...can't say that I'd be doing that...but then again who knows what "the change" will bring.  LOL   Thanks Everyone...can't wait to do it again.
WOOOOOOOOOOO Pinky was the bomb LOL   I say go for it.

Well...I finally got my nerve up and went out on my own.  This is where I went...view from my balcony.  As I'm walking to the water I hear "haha Nancy...what do you think you're doing".  I responded with ...  "getting breakfast".    So there I am fishing...I can feel nibbles...lost one lure to a snag...more nibbles...lost a lure to the darn fish...I'm thinking it must be real BIG.  I sit...re-tie...can hear more hassling from my friend Erika..."no luck Nance"  "haha".   I'm thinking...just wait...I'll show ya.  30 minutes later...after a few more nibbles..."Fish On".   Geeezzz instant heart race.    So I yell.."Hey Erika, I got one!! come give me a hand".  So happy she did come...I had never taken a fish off the hook...then I'm getting nervous about the time the fish is out of the water...have to take pictures...don't forget the OFC sign...oh crap the measuring tape...now I have to hold it too...and then the release.     Erica does the release...come on fishy, breathe...   My friend Erica...say what girl...haha  I hear a male tenant say..."did she really get one"  haha....Yeppers I really did...an 18.5" pike...my first pike
congrats on your first
That's awesome. Congrats..
WTG girl, you'll always remember the 1st one
right on, sounds like fun, and always great to catch a new species for the books
Great report and pics!!!  Congrats on yer first Rot Snocket!!!
WTG.  Congrats on your first pike  Great report and pics
Congrats and thanks for sharing. Good job.
Congrats on your first pike! Its always a thrill to catch a new species.
wtg nancy!!!!!!  sure feels fun catchin.......great sho.....keep at it!!

Thanks Everyone...my day got even better.  As a thank you for helping me with the fish...Erika convinced me to ride with her on her motorcycle....last time I was on one was when I was 19 and the guy went very slow. Well...I had an hour and a half of pure freedom.  I think I'm in for an awesome summer....fishing and riding.
nice pike! congrats on your first!
Awesome twilight, great catching a new species, thanx for sharing.
Awesome!!!....  Congrats Nancy...  G
Congrats on your first pike.
Way to go Nancy, you go girl.  That's awesome.  You should probably use a leader next time, then you won't get bitten off, which pike are notorious for.  Joey
Helluva report!!!  Good for ya!!  Show 'em all!
Congrats on your first Snot Log!!!
WTG Nancy congrats on catching your first ever pike.  So when are you buying a Bike

WTG Nancy thats awesome.  Great report love the photo's.  Nothing like riding on a open road i used to  ride back in the early eighties before i became a mom.    Then i had to give up the bikes.  I often think about getting another bike .  Especially when the friday 13th events roll around here in dover.....   Congrats on your 1st pike hun.
On my 50th BDay .. with pink leather chaps
Congrats on your first piKe!!

Congrats on your first pike!!!  I'm a bit jealous...you got to go fishing, I got to drive 6 hours to Michigan on Saturday to see the in-laws, and then 6 hours on Sunday to come home....LOL.  Great report...hope to see more in the near future!
Congrats on your first pike!

lol Nancy.  Are you going to get the bike to match the chaps?  Have a biker chic that comes to the 13th she rides a bright pink trike  wears all leather pink & white. And seriously this woman has a chest on her bigger than dolly herself......LOL.......wears a very very low v necked leather top and likes to stand with one leg up wearing white leather thigh high boots on her seat, bent over and basically polishes her tank all day.......LOL......  I get such a larf watching the men all standing around like little puppy dogs with there tounges all hanging out and i am sure they're tails are wagging too.....LOL.  Gotta love FRIDAY THE 13TH........lol
